The '''Vershyi Corporation''' was a weapons manufacturer known for its long-range weapons development teams. They had brought many weapons on the military market, but the [[Vershyi Sharpshooter]] was considered one of their best weapon.<ref name="SWG:VS">{{SWGcite|exp=RotW|type=item|Vershyi Sharpshooter}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The Vershyi Corporation was mentioned in the [[2003]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'', a [[Wikipedia:Massively multiplayer online role-playing game|massively multiplayer online roleplaying game]] developed by [[Sony]] Online Entertainment and published by [[LucasArts]],<ref name="SWG:VS" /> prior to its closure on [[December 15]], [[2011]].<ref name="Shutdown">{{SonyCite|url=playerinfo|text=IMPORTANT INFORMATION ABOUT ''STAR WARS'' GALAXIES™}}</ref> The Vershyi Corporation was only mentioned in the description text of the [[Vershyi Sharpshooter]], a weapon added to the game with the release of the expansion pack [[Star Wars Galaxies: Rage of the Wookiees|''Rage of the Wookiees'']] on [[May 5]], [[2005]].<ref name="SWG:VS" />

